John W. Snow - Wikipedia





















 






John W. Snow

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with Jon Snow (character).


John W. Snow








73rd United States Secretary of the Treasury


In office
February 3, 2003 – June 28, 2006


President
George W. Bush


Preceded by
Paul O'Neill


Succeeded by
Henry Paulson





Personal details


